Paper: hep-th/0005203

Date: 2000-05-22

Title: Note on the dual BRST Symmetry in U(1) Gauge Theory

Comments: 12 pages, latex

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A17 (2002) 319-326

We analyze the relation between the Lagrangian and Hamiltonian BRST symmetrygenerators for a recently proposed two-dimensional symmetry. In particular itis shown that this symmetry may be obtained from a canonical transformation inthe ghost sector in a gauge independent way.